quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Yaqeenan falaah payi hai iman laney walon ne jo
  23,2,Apni namaz mein khushu ikhtiyar karte hain (Salat with humility)
  23,3,Laghviyat (vain things) se door rehte hain
  23,4,Zakaat ke tareeqe par aamil hotey hain
  23,5,Apni sharmgaahon ki hifazat karte hain
  23,6,Siwaye apni biwiyon ke aur un auraton ke jo unki milk e yameen mein hon (right hand posseses) ke unpar (mehfooz na rakhne mein) woh qabil e malamat nahin hain
  23,7,Albatta jo uske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi zyadati karne waley hain
  23,8,Apni amanaton (trusts) aur apne ahad o paiman (promises) ka paas rakhte hain
  23,9,Aur apni namazon ki muhafizat (hifazat) karte hain
  23,10,Yahi log woh waris hain
  23,11,Jo miraas mein firdous payenge aur usmein hamesha rahenge
  23,12,Humne Insaan ko mitti ke saatt (essence of clay) se banaya
  23,13,Phir usey ek mehfooz jaga tapki hui boondh mein tabdeel kiya
  23,14,"Phir us boondh ko lothday ki shakal di, phir lothday ko boti bana diya, phir boti ki haddiyan (bones) banayin, phir haddiyon par gosht chadhaya. Phir usey ek dusri hi makhlooq bana khada kiya. Pas bada hi ba-barakat hai Allah, sab karigaron se accha kaarigar(creator)"
  23,15,Phir iske baad tumko zaroor marna hai
  23,16,Phir qayamat ke roz yaqeenan tum uthaye jaogey
  23,17,"Aur tumhare upar humne saat (seven) raastey banaye, takhleeq ke kaam se hum kuch na-balad na thay (We are never unmindful of (our) Creation"
  23,18,Aur aasmaan se humne theek hisaab ke mutabiq ek khaas miqdar mein pani utara aur usko zameen mein thehara diya. Hum usey jis tarah chahein gayab kar sakte hain
  23,19,"Phir is pani ke zariye se humne tumhare liye khajoor aur angoor ke baagh paida kardiye, tumhare liye in baaghon mein bahut se lazeez phal hain aur unsey tum rozi haasil karte ho"
  23,20,"Aur woh darakht bhi humne paida kiya jo Tur-e-seena (mount sinai) se nikalta hai, teil (oil) bhi liye huey ugta hai aur khane walon ke liye saalan bhi"
  23,21,"Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhare liye maweshiyon mein bhi ek sabaq hai unke paithon (bellies) mein jo kuch hai usi mein se ek cheez hum tumhein pilatey hain, aur tumhare liye unmein bahut se dusre faiyde bhi hain"
  23,22,Unko tum khate ho aur unpar aur kashtiyon par sawaar bhi kiye jatey ho